# Get Some Puzzle Release Notes

## Unreleased

* New "Eyes" constraint: a cell counts how many cells of a given color it sees in straight lines
* Equilibrium: first version of the equilibrium-based difficulty signal
* Adapt-to-player improvements (smoother level progression)
* Generator: better puzzle quality, no longer shrinks constraints because of DF
* Hints: improved hint system and fixed a race in hint worker cancellation

## 0.0.1 (13 Aug 2025)

* Initial release
